                         California Resources Agency



   Michael Sweeney
   California Resources Agency




   Undersecretary
   1999 -- Undersecretary for the Resources Agency
   1994-1998 Member, California State Assembly
   Chair, Local Government Commission
   1990-1994 Mayor, City of Hayward
   1982-1990 Member, Hayward City Council
   1984-1994 Member, Alameda County Waste Management Authority
   1984-1994 Member, Board of Directors, Local Government Commission
   Teacher, Hayward Adult School
   EDUCATION
   1974 MA, Political Science - California State University, Hayward
   1972 BA, Political Science - California State University, Hayward



